Class WebotsCommandExecutionVisitor

at.jku.swe.simcomp.webotsadaptor.service.WebotsCommandExecutionVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
at.jku.swe.simcomp.commons.adaptor.execution.command.visitor.ExecutionCommandVisitor<at.jku.swe.simcomp.commons.adaptor.dto.ExecutionResultDTO,String>
@Service public class WebotsCommandExecutionVisitor extends at.jku.swe.simcomp.commons.adaptor.execution.command.visitor.CommandExecutionVisitor
Class to implement the visitor pattern for the supported command types. For each command type a visitor method is implemented, that executes the command with the respective command executor.
